'''Dungalef''' (anagram of the name "Felagund") was the name [[Finrod|Finrod Felagund]] took upon himself during the [[Quest for the Silmaril]] when disguised as an [[Orcs|orc]].  His companion, [[Beren|Beren Erchamion]], took the name of [[Nereb]].<ref name="LB">{{LB|C7}}, p. 229</ref>
